{{Quote|We're in space, Sis. You can't go outside the ship while we're in space!''"<br />"''What do you think spacesuits are for?|[[Milo Graf|Milo]] and Lina Graf|<ref name="Adventures in Wild Space: The Snare">''[[Adventures in Wild Space: The Snare]]''</ref>}}
'''Environment suits''', also known as '''spacesuits''', '''EVA suits''', '''atmospheric suits''', '''vac suits''', '''g-suits''', '''exosuits''', '''enviro-suits''',  an '''envirosuit''', or a '''space suit''',<ref name="A Valiant Vow">''[[The High Republic: A Valiant Vow]]''</ref> were pressure suits that enabled wearers to survive and [[Space walk|operate]] in zero [[gravity]] [[Realspace|space]] and other dangerous conditions such as [[poison]]ous gas or deep [[ocean]] [[water]]. They provided breathing substance—such as [[oxygen]]—and maintained necessary pressure inside the suit. The [[Resistance]] [[pilot]]s [[Poe Dameron]], [[Iolo Arana]], and [[Karé Kun]] donned EVA suits during [[Operation: Sabre Strike]].<ref name="BtA">''[[Before the Awakening]]''</ref>

